rivate equity. But that is <i>precisely </i>why MSNBC wants=E2=80=94indeed,=
 <i>needs</i>=E2=80=94to keep Maddow in its stable and justify its affiliat=
e fees in this brave new world. =E2=80=9CThe spinoff makes her more valuabl=
